==生理功能==
補充ω-3脂肪酸與降低總死亡率之間的關聯目前看來尚未有定論。<ref name=JAMA2017>{{cite journal | vauthors = Rizos EC, Elisaf MS | title = Does Supplementation with Omega-3 PUFAs Add to the Prevention of Cardiovascular Disease? | journal = Current Cardiology Reports | volume = 19 | issue = 6 | pages = 47 | date = June 2017 | pmid = 28432658 | doi = 10.1007/s11886-017-0856-8 | s2cid = 23585060 }}</ref><ref name="JAMA2018">{{cite journal | vauthors = Aung T, Halsey J, Kromhout D, Gerstein HC, Marchioli R, Tavazzi L, Geleijnse JM, Rauch B, Ness A, Galan P, Chew EY, Bosch J, Collins R, Lewington S, Armitage J, Clarke R | display-authors = 6 | title = Associations of Omega-3 Fatty Acid Supplement Use With Cardiovascular Disease Risks: Meta-analysis of 10 Trials Involving 77 917 Individuals | journal = JAMA Cardiology | volume = 3 | issue = 3 | pages = 225–234 | date = March 2018 | pmid = 29387889 | pmc = 5885893 | doi = 10.1001/jamacardio.2017.5205 }}</ref>

ω-3脂肪酸可能降低心血管疾病危險性的機制包括：減少血栓形成、降低血中三酸甘油脂、減緩動脈粥瘤斑的生成、改善內皮細胞功能、輕微降低血壓並抑制發炎反應。如過量攝取ω-3脂肪酸會降低凝血力，有些人會血流不止，所以宜尋求醫師指示，務必小心使用。增加摄入像ALA这样的ω-3脂肪可减少关节、消化道、肺部和大脑的炎症。<ref>{{Cite web|title=吃什么补充维生素f，维生素f是什么东西，维生素f有什么作用|url=http://webmd.cn/2019/11/vitamin-f/|accessdate=2019-11-13|work=WebMD|language=zh-CN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113204531/http://webmd.cn/2019/11/vitamin-f/|archive-date=2019-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 健康影響 ==

=== 癌症 ===
ω-3脂肪酸的攝取已被證實可以降低罹患[[乳癌|乳癌]]的風險。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Omega-3 Fatty Acids|url=https://ods.od.nih.gov/factsheets/Omega3FattyAcids-HealthProfessional/|access-date=2022-03-25|date=2021-08-04|publisher=National Institutes of Health|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523143158/https://ods.od.nih.gov/factsheets/Omega3FattyAcids-HealthProfessional/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Intake of fish and marine n-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids and risk of breast cancer: meta-analysis of data from 21 independent prospective cohort studies|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1136/bmj.f3706|last=Zheng|first=J.-S.|last2=Hu|first2=X.-J.|date=2013-06-27|journal=BMJ|issue=jun27 5|doi=10.1136/bmj.f3706|volume=346|pages=f3706–f3706|issn=1756-1833|last3=Zhao|first3=Y.-M.|last4=Yang|first4=J.|last5=Li|first5=D.}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite journal|title=Dietary conjugated linoleic acid and long-chainn-3 fatty acids in mammary and prostate cancer protection: a review|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.3109/09637486.2011.598849|last=Heinze|first=Verónica M.|last2=Actis|first2=Adriana B.|date=2011-07-15|journal=International Journal of Food Sciences and Nutrition|issue=1|doi=10.3109/09637486.2011.598849|volume=63|pages=66–78|issn=0963-7486}}</ref>然而截至2020，尚未有明確證據證實ω-3脂肪酸的攝取與降低其他癌症風險之間的連結。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3, omega-6 and total dietary polyunsaturated fat on cancer incidence: systematic review and meta-analysis of randomised trials|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/s41416-020-0761-6|last=Hanson|first=Sarah|last2=Thorpe|first2=Gabrielle|date=2020-02-29|journal=British Journal of Cancer|issue=8|doi=10.1038/s41416-020-0761-6|volume=122|pages=1260–1270|issn=0007-0920|last3=Winstanley|first3=Lauren|last4=Abdelhamid|first4=Asmaa S.|last5=Hooper|first5=Lee}}</ref>

對於攝護腺癌的影響尚未有定論。<ref name=":0" /><ref name="#1"/>血液中高濃度的二十二碳五烯酸（DPA）會降低風險，但高濃度的[[二十碳五烯酸|二十碳五烯酸（EPA）]]和[[二十二碳六烯酸|二十二碳六烯酸（DHA）]]可能會增加罹患惡性攝護腺癌的風險。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The relevance of serum levels of long chain omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids and prostate cancer risk: A Meta-analysis|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.5489/cuaj.1056|last=Chua|first=Michael|last2=Sio|first2=M.C.D.|date=2013-05-13|journal=Canadian Urological Association Journal|issue=5-6|doi=10.5489/cuaj.1056|volume=7|pages=333|issn=1920-1214|last3=Sorongon|first3=M.C.|last4=Morales Jr.|first4=M.L.}}</ref>

對於進行癌癌症晚期與惡病體質患者，ω-3脂肪酸的攝取可能可以幫助增進胃口、體重和提升生活品質。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=n-3 Fatty acids, cancer and cachexia: a systematic review of the literature|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1017/s000711450765795x|last=Colomer|first=Ramón|last2=Moreno-Nogueira|first2=José M.|date=2007-05|journal=British Journal of Nutrition|issue=5|doi=10.1017/s000711450765795x|volume=97|pages=823–831|issn=0007-1145|last3=García-Luna|first3=Pedro P.|last4=García-Peris|first4=Pilar|last5=García-de-Lorenzo|first5=Abelardo|last6=Zarazaga|first6=Antonio|last7=Quecedo|first7=Luis|last8=del Llano|first8=Juan|last9=Usán|first9=Luis}}</ref>

=== 心血管疾病 ===
在2020的研究中，有中至高度的證據強度指出，在ω-3多元不飽和脂肪酸中含有的二十碳五烯酸（EPA）和二十二碳六烯酸（DHA），對於死亡率與心血管健康並無顯著的幫助。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 fatty acids for the primary and secondary prevention of cardiovascular disease|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd003177.pub5|last=Abdelhamid|first=Asmaa S|last2=Brown|first2=Tracey J|date=2020-02-29|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=3|doi=10.1002/14651858.cd003177.pub5|volume=2020|issn=1465-1858|last3=Brainard|first3=Julii S|last4=Biswas|first4=Priti|last5=Thorpe|first5=Gabrielle C|last6=Moore|first6=Helen J|last7=Deane|first7=Katherine HO|last8=Summerbell|first8=Carolyn D|last9=Worthington|first9=Helen V}}</ref>

在一篇2018的統合分析中，對於曾有冠狀動脈心臟病史的患者，並沒有找到顯著證據支持每日攝取一克ω-3脂肪酸對預防致命的冠狀動脈心臟病、非致命心肌梗塞或中風有幫助。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Associations of Omega-3 Fatty Acid Supplement Use With Cardiovascular Disease Risks|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1001/jamacardio.2017.5205|last=Aung|first=Theingi|last2=Halsey|first2=Jim|date=2018-03-01|journal=JAMA Cardiology|issue=3|doi=10.1001/jamacardio.2017.5205|volume=3|pages=225|issn=2380-6583|last3=Kromhout|first3=Daan|last4=Gerstein|first4=Hertzel C.|last5=Marchioli|first5=Roberto|last6=Tavazzi|first6=Luigi|last7=Geleijnse|first7=Johanna M.|last8=Rauch|first8=Bernhard|last9=Ness|first9=Andrew}}</ref>然而，若每日攝取超過一克的ω-3脂肪酸且持續超過一年，對於曾有心血管疾病病史的人罹患心臟性猝死和心肌梗塞有保護效果。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Long-term effect of high dose omega-3 fatty acid supplementation for secondary prevention of cardiovascular outcomes: A meta-analysis of randomized, double blind, placebo controlled trials|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s1567-5688(13)70005-9|last=Casula|first=Manuela|last2=Soranna|first2=Davide|date=2013-08|journal=Atherosclerosis Supplements|issue=2|doi=10.1016/s1567-5688(13)70005-9|volume=14|pages=243–251|issn=1567-5688|last3=Catapano|first3=Alberico L.|last4=Corrao|first4=Giovanni}}</ref>

對沒有定期吃魚類的族群，尤其在非裔美國人族群中，ω-3脂肪酸的攝取也有保護心血管健康的效果。<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=You and the Doctor|title=The Harvard Medical School Health Letter Book|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.4159/harvard.9780674593084.c7|publisher=Harvard University Press|date=1981-12-31|pages=395–426}}</ref>

=== 中風 ===
跟據[[考科藍|考科藍合作組織]]在2018年發表的研究指出，ω-3脂肪酸的攝取（攝取量介於0.5至5公克／每日）對於中風的發生率並沒有顯著的影響。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 fatty acids for the primary and secondary prevention of cardiovascular disease|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd003177.pub4|last=Abdelhamid|first=Asmaa S|last2=Brown|first2=Tracey J|date=2018-11-30|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|doi=10.1002/14651858.cd003177.pub4|issn=1465-1858|last3=Brainard|first3=Julii S|last4=Biswas|first4=Priti|last5=Thorpe|first5=Gabrielle C|last6=Moore|first6=Helen J|last7=Deane|first7=Katherine HO|last8=AlAbdulghafoor|first8=Fai K|last9=Summerbell|first9=Carolyn D}}</ref>

=== 免疫系統與發炎 ===
在2013的系統性研究顯示omega−3 fatty acids在健康成人中有益於降低發炎狀況。在服用omega−3 fatty acids後，一些血液中的發炎物質如C-reactive protein, interleukin 6, 以及 TNF alpha有下降的情形。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Effect of Marine-Derived n-3 Polyunsaturated Fatty Acids on C-Reactive Protein, Interleukin 6 and Tumor Necrosis Factor α: A Meta-Analysis|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0088103|last=Li|first=Kelei|last2=Huang|first2=Tao|date=2014-02-05|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=2|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0088103|volume=9|pages=e88103|issn=1932-6203|last3=Zheng|first3=Jusheng|last4=Wu|first4=Kejian|last5=Li|first5=Duo}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Inflammation and its resolution in coronary artery disease: a tightrope walk between omega-6 and omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.33963/kp.15202|last=Artiach|first=Gonzalo|last2=Sarajlic|first2=Philip|date=2020-02-25|journal=Kardiologia Polska|issue=2|doi=10.33963/kp.15202|volume=78|pages=93–95|issn=1897-4279|last3=Bäck|first3=Magnus}}</ref>

針對類風濕性關節炎這種自體免疫疾病，有一篇2012年發表的系統性回顧提到針對「關節腫脹及疼痛、手部關節在早上時的僵硬情形」等症狀是有效果的。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Influence of marinen-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids on immune function and a systematic review of their effects on clinical outcomes in rheumatoid arthritis|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1017/s0007114512001560|last=Miles|first=Elizabeth A.|last2=Calder|first2=Philip C.|date=2012-05-17|journal=British Journal of Nutrition|issue=S2|doi=10.1017/s0007114512001560|volume=107|pages=S171–S184|issn=0007-1145}}</ref>美國風濕病學會提及食用魚油對於類風濕性關節炎有所助益，然而是沒有辦法幾天內立即看到效果的產生．要有效果通常是幾個月以上。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Herbal Remedies, Supplements & Acupuncture for Arthritis|url=https://www.rheumatology.org/i-am-a/patient-caregiver/treatments/herbal-remedies-supplements-acupuncture-for-arthritis|access-date=2020-03-25|date=June 2018|publisher=American College of Rheumatology|archive-date=2022-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220320115559/https://www.rheumatology.org/i-am-a/patient-caregiver/treatments/herbal-remedies-supplements-acupuncture-for-arthritis|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外還要注意食用魚油可能產生對於消化道產生的副作用（容易造成噁心、拉肚子等）。美國國家替代醫學研究中心也有指出omega−3有助於舒緩類風濕性關節炎相關症狀，也提及補充時要注意與當下用藥的搭配，可能會產生交互作用，有血栓的狀況發生。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rheumatoid Arthritis: In-Depth|url=https://nccih.nih.gov/health/RA/getthefacts.htm|access-date=2022-03-25|date=January 2019|publisher=National Center for Complementary and Alternative Medicine|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728123010/https://www.nccih.nih.gov/health/RA/getthefacts.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

截至2021年仍無證據顯示omega−3 fatty acids有助於避免兒童發生免疫反應所引發的慢性呼吸道發炎，也就是氣喘的情形。

=== 發展性障礙 ===
關於omega−3 fatty acids是否有助改善注意力不足過動症的情形仍有爭議：有一篇統合性論文提到補充omega−3 fatty acids有助於改善注意力不足過動症的情形<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 Fatty Acid Supplementation for the Treatment of Children With Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder Symptomatology: Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jaac.2011.06.008|last=Bloch|first=Michael H.|last2=Qawasmi|first2=Ahmad|date=2011-10|journal=Journal of the American Academy of Child & Adolescent Psychiatry|issue=10|doi=10.1016/j.jaac.2011.06.008|volume=50|pages=991–1000|issn=0890-8567}}</ref>，然而有其他文章（考科藍文獻回顧）則是表示並無顯著證據顯示兩者的關聯。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Polyunsaturated fatty acids (PUFA) for attention deficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD) in children and adolescents|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd007986.pub2|last=Gillies|first=Donna|last2=Sinn|first2=John KH|date=2012-07-11|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|doi=10.1002/14651858.cd007986.pub2|issn=1465-1858|last3=Lad|first3=Sagar S|last4=Leach|first4=Matthew J|last5=Ross|first5=Melissa J}}</ref>

2015年發表的一篇統合性分析提到omega−3 fatty acids的補充並沒有助於降低早產率<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 Long Chain Polyunsaturated Fatty Acids to Prevent Preterm Birth|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1097/aog.0000000000000668|last=Saccone|first=Gabriele|last2=Berghella|first2=Vincenzo|date=2015-03|journal=Obstetrics & Gynecology|issue=3|doi=10.1097/aog.0000000000000668|volume=125|pages=663–672|issn=0029-7844}}</ref>，在2018年的考科藍系統性文獻回顧則是提到omega−3 fatty acids是有助於降低生新生兒的產前後死亡、體重過輕的狀況，但有極低可能會有大於胎齡兒<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 fatty acid addition during pregnancy|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd003402.pub3|last=Middleton|first=Philippa|last2=Gomersall|first2=Judith C|date=2018-11-15|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=11|doi=10.1002/14651858.cd003402.pub3|volume=2018|issn=1465-1858|last3=Gould|first3=Jacqueline F|last4=Shepherd|first4=Emily|last5=Olsen|first5=Sjurdur F|last6=Makrides|first6=Maria}}</ref>（指出生體重在同胎齡同性別平均體重的第90百分位以上的嬰兒）。

2021年的傘狀評論則是表示omega−3 fatty acids在懷孕時期的補充有助於避免子癲前症、新生兒體重過輕、早產以及產後憂鬱症，對於胎兒的免疫系統、視力有所幫助，對於產婦則可降低心臟代謝相關危險因子。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The effects of omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids supplementation in pregnancy, lactation, and infancy: An umbrella review of meta-analyses of randomized trials|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.phrs.2022.106100|last=Firouzabadi|first=Fatemeh Dehghani|last2=Shab-Bidar|first2=Sakineh|date=2022-03|journal=Pharmacological Research|doi=10.1016/j.phrs.2022.106100|volume=177|pages=106100|issn=1043-6618|last3=Jayedi|first3=Ahmad}}</ref>

=== 心理健康 ===
關於omega−3 fatty acids是否有助於心理健康則存在許多爭議，在焦慮、重性憂鬱症、思覺失調症等心理健康相關疾病並沒有顯著效果。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 and polyunsaturated fat for prevention of depression and anxiety symptoms: systematic review and meta-analysis of randomised trials|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1192/bjp.2019.234|last=Deane|first=Katherine H. O.|last2=Jimoh|first2=Oluseyi F.|date=2019-10-24|journal=The British Journal of Psychiatry|issue=3|doi=10.1192/bjp.2019.234|volume=218|pages=135–142|issn=0007-1250|last3=Biswas|first3=Priti|last4=O'Brien|first4=Alex|last5=Hanson|first5=Sarah|last6=Abdelhamid|first6=Asmaa S.|last7=Fox|first7=Chris|last8=Hooper|first8=Lee}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The efficacy and safety of nutrient supplements in the treatment of mental disorders: a meta‐review of meta‐analyses of randomized controlled trials|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/wps.20672|last=Firth|first=Joseph|last2=Teasdale|first2=Scott B.|date=2019-09-09|journal=World Psychiatry|issue=3|doi=10.1002/wps.20672|volume=18|pages=308–324|issn=1723-8617|last3=Allott|first3=Kelly|last4=Siskind|first4=Dan|last5=Marx|first5=Wolfgang|last6=Cotter|first6=Jack|last7=Veronese|first7=Nicola|last8=Schuch|first8=Felipe|last9=Smith|first9=Lee|access-date=2022-03-25|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728031727/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1002/wps.20672|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年的考科藍文獻回顧點出針對重性憂鬱症，omega−3 fatty acids也無顯著治療效果。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 fatty acids for depression in adults|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd004692.pub5|last=Appleton|first=Katherine M|last2=Voyias|first2=Philip D|date=2021-11-24|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=11|doi=10.1002/14651858.cd004692.pub5|volume=2021|issn=1465-1858|last3=Sallis|first3=Hannah M|last4=Dawson|first4=Sarah|last5=Ness|first5=Andrew R|last6=Churchill|first6=Rachel|last7=Perry|first7=Rachel}}</ref>也有研究顯示omega−3 fatty acids被使用在躁鬱症的治療上，然而並沒有足夠數據可以加強他的實證強度。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3 fatty acids for bipolar disorder|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd005169|last=Montgomery|first=P|last2=Richardson|first2=AJ|date=2004-07-19|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|location=Chichester, UK|last3=Ross|first3=MA}}</ref>

關於為什麼如此難以界定是否有沒有效果，最主要是因為要受試者回憶過去的飲食是否含有omega−3 fatty acids存在誤差，另外每個研究在定義是否屬於可以補充omega−3 fatty acids的食物來源難以有一個統一的標準。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Diet and the risk of unipolar depression in adults: systematic review of cohort studies|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1365-277x.2012.01283.x|last=Sanhueza|first=C.|last2=Ryan|first2=L.|date=2012-10-18|journal=Journal of Human Nutrition and Dietetics|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1365-277x.2012.01283.x|volume=26|pages=56–70|issn=0952-3871|last3=Foxcroft|first3=D. R.}}</ref>

=== 認知功能老化 ===
研究並無顯示omega−3 fatty acids和阿茲海默症、失智症治療並無關聯<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega 3 fatty acids for the treatment of dementia|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/14651858.cd009002.pub2|last=Burckhardt|first=Marion|last2=Herke|first2=Max|date=2015-03-10|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|location=Chichester, UK|last3=Wustmann|first3=Tobias|last4=Watzke|first4=Stefan|last5=Langer|first5=Gero|last6=Fink|first6=Astrid}}</ref>，而在2020有一篇文章顯示補充omega−3 fatty acids對於認知功能老化並無影響，唯在並未失智的成人上有促進記憶的輕微助益。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Long-chain omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acids and cognitive decline in non-demented adults: a systematic review and meta-analysis|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/nutrit/nuz073|last=Alex|first=Anu|last2=Abbott|first2=Kylie A|date=2019-12-16|journal=Nutrition Reviews|issue=7|doi=10.1093/nutrit/nuz073|volume=78|pages=563–578|issn=0029-6643|last3=McEvoy|first3=Mark|last4=Schofield|first4=Peter W|last5=Garg|first5=Manohar L}}</ref>

=== 大腦、視覺功能 ===
二十二碳六烯酸（DHA）作爲哺乳類動物的大腦中的主要組成物之一，同時也是大腦中含量最多的ω-3脂肪酸。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Nutrition for the Brain: Commentary on the article by Isaacs et al. on page 308|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1203/pdr.0b013e318168c6d1|last=Hüppi|first=Petra S|date=2008-03|journal=Pediatric Research|issue=3|doi=10.1203/pdr.0b013e318168c6d1|volume=63|pages=229–231|issn=0031-3998}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=HEALTH BENEFITS OF DOCOSAHEXAENOIC ACID (DHA)|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1006/phrs.1999.0495|last=HORROCKS|first=LLOYD A.|last2=YEO|first2=YOUNG K.|date=1999-09|journal=Pharmacological Research|issue=3|doi=10.1006/phrs.1999.0495|volume=40|pages=211–225|issn=1043-6618}}</ref>腦功能與視覺的運作仰賴飲食攝入的二十二碳六烯酸（DHA）來維持多樣的細胞膜功能，尤其在灰質中。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA): An Ancient Nutrient for the Modern Human Brain|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.3390/nu3050529|last=Bradbury|first=Joanne|date=2011-05-10|journal=Nutrients|issue=5|doi=10.3390/nu3050529|volume=3|pages=529–554|issn=2072-6643}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Beyond building better brains: bridging the docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) gap of prematurity|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/jp.2014.195|last=Harris|first=W S|last2=Baack|first2=M L|date=2014-10-30|journal=Journal of Perinatology|issue=1|doi=10.1038/jp.2014.195|volume=35|pages=1–7|issn=0743-8346}}</ref>

=== 糖尿病 ===
目前並無顯著研究顯示omega−3 fatty acids有辦法預防第二型糖尿病。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Omega-3, omega-6, and total dietary polyunsaturated fat for prevention and treatment of type 2 diabetes mellitus: systematic review and meta-analysis of randomised controlled trials|author=Brown T J|url=|journal=BMJ|others=Brainard J, Song F, Wang X, Abdelhamid A, Hooper L.|year=2019}}</ref>在2018一篇文章指出，現今臨床試驗結果並不支持補充omega−3 fatty acids作為改善血糖的控制，且關於糖尿病腎臟病變、視網膜病變患者並無建議攝取omega−3 fatty acids這樣的指引。

=== 苯酮尿症 ===
通常在苯酮尿症患者上可以觀察到低omega−3 fatty acids攝取的情形，原因是因為他們體內蛋白質的代謝受到影響，因此不能攝取太多高蛋白的食物，導致攝入富含omega−3 fatty acids的食物機會大幅降低（如深海魚類）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Lower n-3 long-chain polyunsaturated fatty acid values in patients with phenylketonuria: a systematic review and meta-analysis|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.nutres.2013.05.003|last=Lohner|first=Szimonetta|last2=Fekete|first2=Katalin|date=2013-07|journal=Nutrition Research|issue=7|doi=10.1016/j.nutres.2013.05.003|volume=33|pages=513–520|issn=0271-5317|last3=Decsi|first3=Tamás}}</ref>

=== 治療COVID19 ===
在2021年有一篇隨機臨床試驗文章<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Impact of Omega-3 Fatty Acid Supplementation on Memory Functions in Healthy Older Adults|url=https://www.medra.org/servlet/aliasResolver?alias=iospress&doi=10.3233/JAD-150886|last=Külzow|first=Nadine|last2=Witte|first2=A. Veronica|date=2016-03-30|journal=Journal of Alzheimer's Disease|issue=3|doi=10.3233/JAD-150886|editor-last=Anstey|editor-first=Kaarin|volume=51|pages=713–725|last3=Kerti|first3=Lucia|last4=Grittner|first4=Ulrike|last5=Schuchardt|first5=Jan Philipp|last6=Hahn|first6=Andreas|last7=Flöel|first7=Agnes}}</ref>顯示omega−3 脂肪酸的補充可以改善得到COVID-19產生酸中毒以及腎功能方面問題的情形，隨機試驗結果包含實驗組在補充omega−3 脂肪酸血液中的pH值有顯著的高於對照組，然而在PO2 和 PCO2的部分並無顯著差異，實驗組在14天後然而仍然需要更多的臨床試驗、更大的樣本數來確切其療效。
==作用机制==
必需脂肪酸之所以“必需”，是因为研究人员发现，它们在幼儿和幼年动物的成长发育中起到不可或缺的作用。人类大脑含有丰富的二十二碳六烯酸(DHA)，它正是一种ω−3脂肪酸。生成DHA这种物质，需要发生去饱和反应，反应中要用到去饱和酶，在ω−3和ω−6位碳原子上生成双键；但人类正正缺乏去饱和酶。正因如此，ω−3脂肪酸和ω−6脂肪酸都无法在体内合成，必须从食物中摄取；“必需脂肪酸”这个名称，充分反映了这种性质。<br>
1964年，研究人员发现，[[绵羊|绵羊]]组织中有酶，可以把[[花生四烯酸|花生四烯酸]]这种[[Ω-6脂肪酸|ω−6]]转化为[[炎症|炎症]]因子——[[前列腺素|前列腺素]]E<sub>2</sub><ref>{{cite journal |author=Bergstrom, Danielson, Klenberg, and Samuelsson |title=The Enzymatic Conversion of Essential fatty Acids into Prostaglandins |journal=The Journal of Biological Chemistry |volume=239 |issue=11 |pages=PC4006–PC4008 |date=Nov 1964 |url=http://www.jbc.org/content/239/11/PC4006.full.pdf |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007214813/http://www.jbc.org/content/239/11/PC4006.full.pdf |archive-date=2018-10-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>， [[前列腺素|前列腺素]]E<sub>2</sub>与创伤、感染组织发生的免疫应答有关。1979年，科学家进一步发现了[[血栓素|血栓素]]、[[前列环素|前列环素]]、[[白三烯|白三烯]]等统称为[[类花生酸|类花生酸]]的物质<ref name=Lands1992>{{Cite journal | author = Lands, William E.M. | year = 1992 | title = Biochemistry and physiology of ''n''–3 fatty acids | journal = [[FASEB_Journal|FASEB Journal]] | publisher = [[Federation_of_American_Societies_for_Experimental_Biology|Federation of American Societies for Experimental Biology]] | volume = 6 | issue = 8 | pages = 2530–2536 | url = http://www.fasebj.org/content/6/8/2530.full.pdf | pmid = 1592205 | accessdate = 2008-03-21 | authorlink = William E.M. Lands | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111112091135/http://www.fasebj.org/content/6/8/2530.full.pdf | archive-date = 2011-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 类花生酸在体内发生效用的时间较短，由脂肪酸合成而得，最终由酶代谢分解。如果合成的速度大于代谢速度，过量的类花生酸就可能产生不良影响。研究人员发现，某些ω−3脂肪酸也可以合成类花生酸和类二十二碳六烯酸(docosanoids)，但合成速度较低。合成期间，如果ω−6与ω−3脂肪酸同时存在，它们参与合成反应时会发生竞争，因此长链ω−3与ω−6脂肪酸的比例，直接影响合成所得的类花生酸种类。<ref name=Lands1992/>
